dismissalText.commentary: Mahela Udawatte c Mohammad Tauqir b Fahad Alhashmi 67 (74b 6x4 0x6) SR: 90.54

dismissalComment.html: soft dismissal! That was overpitched on middle and he made a bit of room to carve that across the line and over on the on side, the elevation was missing and Tauqir had a very easy take at midwicket

dismissalText.commentary: Mahela Jayawardene run out (Aman Ali) 61 (43b 9x4 0x6) SR: 141.86

dismissalComment.html: outside the off stump, Udawatte steers it to short third man and sets off for a quick single and the fielder throws the stumps down with precision. Third Umpires help is sought and replays suggest that he was out and he flashes the red light

commentTextItems.html: on the off stump, Aman Ali looks to defend it and misses it and is rapped on the pads . Mendis gets his five wicket haul

commentPostTextItems.html: Amjad Ali looked to have started the chase off in earnest, but after the fall of his wicket, UAE just petered away
Saqib, UAE captain says " There are lot of positives to take back "
Ajantha Mendis gets the Man of the match and says"He is pretty excited to be bowling to the premier batsmen"
Mahela says " There are a lot of positives but there are a few areas to be developed too"
Great news for our readers in USA. You can now watch all matches in the Asia Cup live - and for free - on ESPN 360. You can also watch daily match highlights on Cricinfo TV. Click here.
All you Social networking freaks out there, add Cricinfo Widgets to your page
Thats it then for the night

milestones.description: Indika Batuwitarachchi and Amjad Ali's 70-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 33 between Poonawala and Mazhar Hussain
Alhashmi has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for UAE, going past Indika Batuwitarachchi's 1
Khurram Khan has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs for UAE, going past Sameer Zia's 2
This is the highest match aggregate (438) involving teams Sri Lanka & U.A.E. in ODIs
Amjad Ali has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (3) in ODIs for UAE, going past Imtiaz Abbasi's 2
